name: AS_ADT_UT_startAuditProcess
description: Executes a!startProcess to execute an audit on the objects
sail_code:
#"SYSTEM_SYSRULES_startProcess"(
  processModel: cons!AS_ADT_PM_AUDIT_PROCESS,
  processParameters: rule!AS_ADT_UT_startAuditProcess_Parameters(
    newObjects: ri!newObjects,
    objectType: ri!objectType,
    objectDse: ri!objectDse,
    auditDse: ri!auditDse,
    auditConfig: ri!auditConfig
  ),
  onSuccess: {
    a!save(
      ri!processInfo,
      fv!processInfo
    ),
    ri!onSuccess
  },      
  onError: ri!onError
)
